---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import ContentSection from "../components/sections/ContentSection.astro";
---
<Layout title="¡Gracias! · ESIC Medellín">
  <ContentSection z={1} bg="bg-bg" padding="py-24 md:py-32">
    <div class="max-w-[720px] mx-auto text-center">
      <div class="inline-flex w-20 h-20 rounded-full bg-brand-teal grid place-items-center mb-8">
        <svg width="40" height="40" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="white" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
          <path d="M20 6 9 17l-5-5"/>
        </svg>
      </div>
      <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-3 text-[0.74rem] font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.22em] text-brand-blue mb-3">
        <span class="block h-px w-8 bg-current" aria-hidden="true"></span>
        Formulario enviado
      </span>
      <h1 class="font-display text-5xl md:text-6xl font-extrabold uppercase text-brand-blue-dark leading-[0.95]">
        Hemos recibido<br />tu solicitud
      </h1>
      <div class="w-20 h-[2px] bg-brand-blue mx-auto my-8"></div>
      <p class="text-[1.05rem] text-ink-muted leading-relaxed max-w-[55ch] mx-auto">
        Uno de nuestros asesores se pondrá en contacto contigo muy pronto por el medio que
        indicaste. Mientras tanto, puedes seguir explorando los programas.
      </p>
      <div class="mt-10 flex flex-wrap gap-3 justify-center">
        <a href="/" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-brand-blue text-white text-[0.85rem] font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.06em] px-7 py-3 hover:bg-brand-blue-dark transition-colors no-underline">
          Volver al inicio
        </a>
        <a href="/programas/" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-white text-brand-blue-dark text-[0.85rem] font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.06em] px-7 py-3 border border-brand-blue-dark/15 hover:bg-bg-alt transition-colors no-underline">
          Ver programas
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </ContentSection>
</Layout>
